snippet.title: Celeste Mario's Zap & Dash! - Hack of Super Mario Bros. [NES]
snippet.description:
Hack Released By w7n, Morshu , @StudsX , karmic, @Eden_GT 

v1.0 https://www.romhacking.net/hacks/7915/
Release Date: 05 July 2023

Thumbnail Artwork By Bourgy
https://bourgy.net/

A hastily done minihack (with levels designed within 2 months) that features Celeste-styled gameplay.

Controls: 
A: Jump
B: Dash (B is not used for running.)
A while on wall: Wall kick
UP+A while on wall: Wall jump (consumes stamina)


Credits
w7n, Morshu , StudsX, karmic, Eden GT
